Reasoning: The paper deals with the analysis of end-to-end throughput in wireless ad hoc networks, which is a topic related to network protocols and communication systems. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also involves the study of physical layer limitations, medium access control (MAC) protocol properties, routing policy, and nodes’ distribution, which are related to information theory (cs.IT), multi-agent systems (cs.MA), data structures (cs.DS), and control systems (cs.SY).
